roon\" width=\"500\" height=\"100\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[500px] h-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fheader_logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fheader_logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fheader_logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-semibold tracking-wide\">Excellent in schilderwerken</p></div><div class=\"relative lg:absolute lg:-right-12 lg:top-1/2 lg:-translate-y-1/2 lg:w-[45vw] lg:max-w-[600px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(30px)\"><img alt=\"Keizer &amp; De Kroon schilderwerk\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-auto rounded-l-2xl shadow-2xl\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fshowcase-photo.JPEG&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fshowcase-photo.JPEG&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fshowcase-photo.JPEG&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-white/40\"><div class=\"h-10 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-white/30\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"bg-white py-24 md:py-32\" aria-labelledby=\"features-heading\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-24 md:gap-32\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20 lg:flex-row\"><div class=\"flex-1 max-w-[440px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 font-extrabold text-[#3a2313] leading-tight\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem)\">Hoogwaardig Binnenschilderwerk</h2><div class=\"text-[#6b6b6b] leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg\"><p class=\"mb-3\">Keizer &amp; De Kroon verzorgt hoogwaardig binnenschilderwerk voor panden waar uitstraling, detail en afwerking van belang zijn. Onze werkzaamheden vinden voornamelijk plaats in karaktervol commercieel en particulier vastgoed in het centrum van Amsterdam.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[480px]\"><img alt=\"Hoogwaardig binnenschilderwerk\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"480\" height=\"340\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-xl shadow-xl object-cover w-full\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbinnenschilderwerk.JPEG&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbinnenschilderwerk.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbinnenschilderwerk.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20 lg:flex-row-reverse\"><div class=\"flex-1 max-w-[440px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 font-extrabold text-[#3a2313] leading-tight\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem)\">Met oog voor detail</h2><div class=\"text-[#6b6b6b] leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-[#ff656a] mt-1 text-xl\">•</span><span>Gespecialiseerd in schilderwerk voor karaktervol vastgoed</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-[#ff656a] mt-1 text-xl\">•</span><span>Zorgvuldige uitvoering met oog voor detail en afwerking</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-[#ff656a] mt-1 text-xl\">•</span><span>Werkzaamheden afgestemd op panden die in gebruik blijven</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-[#ff656a] mt-1 text-xl\">•</span><span>Heldere planning en duidelijke communicatie</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-[#ff656a] mt-1 text-xl\">•</span><span>Actief in het centrum van Amsterdam en omgeving</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[480px]\"><img alt=\"Waarom Keizer &amp; De Kroon\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"480\" height=\"340\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-xl shadow-xl object-cover w-full\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdetail.JPEG&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdetail.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdetail.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20 lg:flex-row\"><div class=\"flex-1 max-w-[440px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 font-extrabold text-[#3a2313] leading-tight\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem)\">Vastgoedonderhoud</h2><div class=\"text-[#6b6b6b] leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg\"><p class=\"mb-3\">Wij verzorgen professioneel vastgoedonderhoud waarbij kwaliteit en zorgvuldigheid voorop staan. Blijft uw pand in gebruik tijdens onze werkzaamheden? Dan stemmen wij onze werkwijze hier zorgvuldig op af, zodat processen en het dagelijks gebruik zo min mogelijk verstoord worden.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[480px]\"><img alt=\"Professioneel vastgoedonderhoud\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"480\" height=\"340\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-xl shadow-xl object-cover w-full\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fvastgoedonderhoud.JPEG&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fvastgoedonderhoud.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fvastgoedonderhoud.JPEG&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-white border-t border-black/8\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6 py-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><a aria-label=\"Keizer &amp; De Kroon — home\" class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"size-12\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ffavicon.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Ffavicon.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Ffavicon.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"font-bold text-[#111] text-lg\">Keizer &amp; De Kroon</span></a><p class=\"text-sm text-[#6b6b6b] max-w-[260px] leading-relaxed\">Excellent in schilderwerken</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-black/8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4\"><p class=\"text-xs text-[#6b6b6b]\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->Keizer &amp; De Kroon<!-- -->. All rights reserved.</p><a href=\"mailto:info@keizerendekroon.nl\" class=\"text-xs text-[#6b6b6b] hover:text-[#111] transition-colors duration-200\">info@keizerendekroon.nl</a></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><section aria-label=\"Notifications alt+T\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-relevant=\"additions text\" aria-atomic=\"false\"></section><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/98df2cc20320078e.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[3097,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/33074d3ff5d0cd2d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/c4d90098b4abc498.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[99299,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/33074d3ff5d0cd2d.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/c4d90098b4abc498.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[13354,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/e13c50eb0f2505d3.js\\\"],\\\"Toaster\\\"]\\n5:I[66250,[\\\"/_next/